        translation: "O Allah, our Lord, to You is the praise, filling the heavens and the earth, and filling whatever You will besides that. You are the Provider of praise and glory. There is no withholder of what You give, and no giver of what You withhold, and the wealth of a wealthy person does not benefit him against You.",
